ctu.nengoros.rosparam

Class Jrosparam

  • java.lang.Object
    • ctu.nengoros.rosparam.Jrosparam

  • public class Jrosparam
extends java.lang.Object
    This is runnable application which implements subset of functionalities of the original rosparam application.
    See Also:
    rosparam For the first time, it can be used as normal rosparam, so, e.g.:
    • rosparam set [key] [val]
    • rosparam get [key]
    • rosparam list
    • rosparam delete [key]
    but the application stays on and accepts further commands without "jrospram" string, e.g.
    • set [ket] [val]
    • list ..etc
